messages.messageBody:
Hi all, Sessuale J Here :)

Well I did it - finally! I got some of the pictures from my daughter's
Indian Dance Recital up on the net and am trying to finish up my site
on Bharat Natyam *before we leave for India. As you know my company
opens for business in Bangalore, India on the 10th so I am unbelievably
busy! But I am having a problem finding Indian Clip Art. I am specifically
looking for Hindu symbols or dance related clip art.

Can anyone help? Any suggestions are most appreciated!

The site is:

http://beautybeginshere.addr.com/india_classical_dance/

Thanks, Sessuale
